{"tid":998524,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工比同事騷擾可以點做","createTime":"2019-01-28T04:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T05:23:03.000Z","uid":202317,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"830ce47efc273442658e3bab0a3560a68ea57865","tid":998524,"uid":202317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的 就有位男同事一直同佢都有幾句<br />\n到最近返工個3日 佢講啲野開始好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如 我好鍾意染頭髮 最近甩色 我當一般傾計咁問佢幾時補染好 利申：個個同事都有問意見<br />\n佢會同我講唔好染喇 promise我喇好無？<br />\n我就答佢 吓 promise呢樣野我只會對我鍾意個個<br />\n我就走開左 佢就講bb 乖喇 聽話啦<br />\n我吓到即刻對住佢講你都痴線 打撚晒冷震咁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢又聊我傾計 我講到想去旅行 佢無喇喇話陪我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我即刻又係咁講晒粗口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我做咩都會feel到佢望我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都以為我心多 因為條友有女<br />\n後一日返工 佢都係咁聊我講野 又話咩好掛住你呀bb<br />\n我已經好冷淡應佢 哦 吓咁樣<br />\n佢就話我對佢好冷淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩以前我唔係咁 咩對佢好熱情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實只係一般傾下計 只不過無咁冷淡應佢<br />\n仲有好多<br />\n真心問 可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢私下一次msg傾計都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係工作交情"},{"pid":"2043af3daf62595f9281a6382d0dd956cfb19fcd","tid":998524,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"706037c21cf2d1aa2d3c02052831a45478c96403","tid":998524,"uid":210161,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意染頭髮 最近甩色 我當一般傾計咁問佢幾時補染好<br />\n<br />\n依d扮靚話題正常係唔會同男同事傾既...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩promise 依d野只會對住鐘意既人做<br />\n依句都太over&rsquo;....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一睇知係膠post 但忍唔住認真答症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16ddaca8caf61dce064e85edf07774b0d9b30f9","tid":998524,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"租個ptgf<br />\n<br />\n 證明你係直架囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43ace2949525adc9b365d14b14066cfc3cb27b3","tid":998524,"uid":83340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"職場有防性騷擾既條例<br />\n如果佢有更明顯既性暗示字眼，或不當既身體接觸<br />\n你可以同HR投訴<br />\n然後會轉介個案<br />\n假如佢無道歉或唔認，你可以選擇上庭，判得成多數會罰款加賠償"},{"pid":"f2825ec807ad4176443d8f133db203702e5e0a72","tid":998524,"uid":52509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"Promise 嗰度 笑到傻"},{"pid":"f5e7fa31ef9af8f99c2f68b911660143acd79d21","tid":998524,"uid":202317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2825ec807ad4176443d8f133db203702e5e0a72","tid":998524,"uid":52509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"Promise 嗰度 笑到傻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"真心 我個陣答佢係promise 只對鍾意既人做<br />\n所以唔會promise佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e6afa9881d604bef8eada9ea816e5af4a0c695","tid":998524,"uid":6329,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"大家都男人，講d咁既野的確幾嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c9f4da8b14989dda79a840be0f29b4dd61fbde","tid":998524,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"其實要睇下佢既口吻係咪 玩野嗰啲語氣。 有啲男仔其實只係懶幽默， 對埋向錯既對象搞幽靈啫。 <br />\n<